    <item>
      <title>温和通胀支持美联储再次大幅降息，债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bonds-rise-as-mild-inflation-backs-case-for-another-big-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储青睐的美国基本通胀指标小幅上升，增强了交易商对 11 月份再次大幅降息的预期，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bonds-rise-as-mild-inflation-backs-case-for-another-big-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼的目标是到 2026 年将意大利赤字控制在 2.8% 以取悦布鲁塞尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/meloni-targets-italy-deficit-at-2-8-by-2026-to-please-brussels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新财政计划，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼领导的政府计划在两年内将意大利赤字降至 2.8%，该计划还预计在选举前增加支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/meloni-targets-italy-deficit-at-2-8-by-2026-to-please-brussels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:55:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
