    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行的 Orlopp 将加入 UniCredit 的行列，共同规划发展路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/commerzbank-s-orlopp-slated-to-join-unicredit-call-to-chart-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两周前，德国商业银行表示可能试图收购意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA)，而该银行即将上任的首席执行官将与这家规模较小的竞争对手讨论如何合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/commerzbank-s-orlopp-slated-to-join-unicredit-call-to-chart-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息预期和中国刺激措施推动欧洲股市创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-stocks-test-new-highs-as-china-us-fuel-global-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国一系列刺激措施以及越来越多的人相信未来几个月美国和欧元区利率将进一步下降的推动，欧洲股市周五创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-stocks-test-new-highs-as-china-us-fuel-global-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 07:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币摆脱季节性不利因素，9 月份涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bitcoin-btc-heads-to-one-of-best-septembers-on-record-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以美联储为首的全球降息浪潮的帮助下，比特币这一最大的数字资产摆脱了季节性衰退，有望实现 9 月份最大涨幅之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bitcoin-btc-heads-to-one-of-best-septembers-on-record-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应增加前景导致油价周线大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续两天大幅下跌后企稳，由于石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 成员国沙特阿拉伯和利比亚有望增加供应，油价仍将出现本周大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
